{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_背尸",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·背庄家尸（教学：背尸力学 / V2：帕子包·坠潭·死亡系绳）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_背尸",
              "state": "fled",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "不看了。这辈子都不想再看。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "大红嫁衣在烛光底下红得发黑。关二狗啐了口唾沫搓搓手——上前，过肩，搭手。背尸的老把式，闭着眼都不会错。",
      "next": "n_hold"
    },
    "n_hold": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_bride_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "瘫坐在地上喘气的工夫，越缓越觉出不对——这一具，跟他背过的八百具，哪一具都不一样。",
      "next": "n_chant"
    },
    "n_chant": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "凉是凉的，沉是沉的，该是什么——",
      "next": "n_chant2"
    },
    "n_chant2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "那句背了八百回、念顺了的话，卡在了喉咙里。这一具，哪样都不对。",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "凉透骨。重得邪门。停了多日像才刚停下。这尸，哪样都不对劲。头皮一层一层麻上来。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "工钱……工钱个屁！！",
      "next": "n6"
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他连滚带爬夺门而出。没敢回城——顺着官道，闷头往黑里跑。",
      "next": "n_pouch"
    },
    "n_pouch": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "跑出二里地，道旁枯草里露着个旧帕子包，鼓鼓囊囊像裹着值钱货。鬼使神差，他贪心一把抄进怀里——破是破，没舍得扔。",
      "next": "n_pouch_give"
    },
    "n_pouch_give": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveItem",
          "params": {
            "id": "old_cloth_pouch",
            "count": 1
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_pouch_scent"
    },
    "n_pouch_scent": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "揣上那一刻，一缕味儿浮起来——浆洗棉布、线头，和一点……廉价香粉。不知打哪儿来，散不掉。",
      "next": "n_cue"
    },
    "n_cue": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_背尸",
            "signal": "beishi_scent"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "尸臭俺闻过八百回。这味儿——不是。怎么揣上这破包，倒跟上俺了？",
      "next": "n_drown"
    },
    "n_drown": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他越跑越急，脚下猛一空——一头栽进路边深潭。冷水灌进鼻子、耳朵，天光一寸寸缩小。就在要沉到底的当口——",
      "next": "n_drown_act"
    },
    "n_drown_act": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "damagePlayer",
          "params": {
            "amount": 9999
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_drown2"
    },
    "n_drown2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一股看不见的劲，从怀里那个包里漫出来，把他从水底硬生生拽了回来。他呛着水爬上岸，趴在泥里，半条命——身上那缕香粉味，没散。",
      "next": "n_flag"
    },
    "n_flag": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_背尸",
            "signal": "beishi_fled"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldToBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 900
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
